1999;;Lycanthrope;;American;;Bob Cook;;Robert Carradine, Michael Winslow, Rebecca Holden;;horror;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lycanthrope_(film);;A team of scientists are studying ozone depletion while living in a lab in the Amazon Rainforest when they are attacked by a clinical lycanthrope who has gone insane because of over-exposure to the sun's ultraviolet rays, caused by the hole in the ozone layer.